{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9984d644b5","title":"为延安《山脉文学》杂志题写刊头","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a57e4c16f9","index":0,"year":1938,"month":10,"day":27,"articleId":"9984d644b5"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d0133865fb","type":"paragraph","text":"为延安《山脉文学》杂志题写刊头”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"9984d644b5"},{"id":"8c5a60b063","type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年10月27日）山脉文学写下几个字，不知可用否？名称似以“山头文学“为好。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"9984d644b5"},{"id":"32c6343563","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"9984d644b5"},{"id":"9ad18940a4","type":"paragraph","text":"十月二十七日[1]1938年10月下句成立的群众性的“山脉文学社”，提出“十大文艺活动方式”，筹备出版一个以发表青年文艺爱好者诗文习作为主的《山脉文学》不定期刊。吴定怀给毛泽东写能，向他报告进一步开展群众性抗战文艺活动的打算，并请他为《山脉文学》题写刊头。毛泽东为共题写了刊头。后来，由于印刷条件未获解决，《山脉文学》未能出版，而是或出了油印的《山脉诗歌》。这样，便出现了“山脉诗酸社”。而山款文学社的活动则持续到1940年9月。见行的的在安：如长计心红大平内期。振大：","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"9984d644b5"},{"id":"ade93a92eb","type":"paragraph","text":"文高","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"9984d644b5"},{"id":"a71cc7d9b4","type":"paragraph","text":"路毛泽东给山脉文学社的复信和为《山脉文学》题写的刊头","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"9984d644b5"}],"page":{"id":"bfcda8be52","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"9984d644b5","start":26,"end":27}}}},"__N_SSG":true}